All experiments validating the proposed HFID methodology were conducted on a workstation with NVIDIA Tesla T4 GPUs, enabling robust computation for deep-learning tasks. Python, along with the PyTorch framework \cite{paszke2019pytorch}, served as the primary programming environment, utilizing various open-source libraries for implementation and evaluation.
